  "body": "**Steps to reproduce**\r\n1. Copy some long text into buffer\r\n2. Open 1-1 chat\r\n3. Paste the text into textbox -> tap ‘send’ button\r\n4. Paste the text into textbox one more time\r\n5. Try to expand textbox manually\r\n\r\n**Actual result**\r\n- The textbox is not fully expanded after step 4\r\n- The textbox is not able to be expanded manually. It is luggy after each attempting to expand it\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52490791/207575967-3b6b9bc5-cfeb-4fd1-ba3b-e831238d66e7.mp4\r\n\r\n**Expected result**\r\n- The textbox is expanded properly related to the size of the pasted text\r\n- The current text field can be easily extended manually\r\n\r\n**ENV:** Samsung Galaxy S20+ v10, Huawei p20 light\r\n\r\n\r\n",
